title: 2014 - The Year In Christian Music (Bundle 49)
description:
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
2014 - THE YEAR IN CHRISTIAN MUSIC
-----------------------------------------------------------------------

I enjoyed my time on Christian Tunes.  Thank you to all of you who joined us over there.  And thank you to all of you who were able to contribute to the enrichment of that website, whether it was through dialog, sharing your own music, fellowship, etc.  But I'm back here on The Pirate Bay now.  Meaning I have no intention of doing any more sharing on Christian Tunes.

This is a double bundle offering today.  By that, I mean it's 4 gigs in file size, and not the usual 2 gigabyte limit.  Because of that, I suspect it will take longer than normal to fully seed.  So please be patient.

When I left The Pirate Bay in August, I mentioned that I wouldn't be torrenting music here, that I was file sharing over there on Christian Tunes.  I've since rethought me position on that.  And if there's enough interest here for me to do so, and if I have enough time to do so, I may try to create bundles for those 2014 albums I was able to either share, or download from Christian Tunes.  But I'll let you guys decide the direction on that.

Our year-to-date total is now up to 1683.  That surpasses the 1669 we shared in 2013.

We are sharing 47 titles amongst ourselves today, including...
